般而言，若該人士於遞交樣本後的三天內未有接獲通知，即表示其樣本對檢測呈陰性反應<br />\no 如果樣本瓶及化驗表格上印有條碼，一般情況下，該人士會在遞交樣本後的三天內會收到電話短訊通知</span><br />\n若檢測經由私家醫生轉介，詳情可以向你的私家醫生查詢<br />\n更多詳情: <a href=\"https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLudqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=a0bb757a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a> <br />\n更多防疫資訊，請瀏覽2019冠狀病毒病專題網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLudqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=42b247d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"28f201ec84e8409a2148dfb88e8487914cee59f4","tid":2407131,"uid":231352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"我都係11號交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日十一點收到"},{"pid":"0a33f006570efafb2c44ea0510af70f4803766a3","tid":2407131,"uid":231352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"11號交樽仔講個個人講最遲初四加三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6f44b1b97db799bf9385559782af2787bd7867","tid":2407131,"uid":273006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28f201ec84e8409a2148dfb88e8487914cee59f4","tid":2407131,"uid":231352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"我都係11號交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日十一點收到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:06:25.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇餐死"},{"pid":"b1f3cf8d31150ebde0abc697ed2cecd4c597cff2","tid":2407131,"uid":273006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0be74acbae026ae8aed6cc6d584c8823a38a2b3","tid":2407131,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot